// EventCTA Component - Call-to-action section with features
---

<section id="cta-section">
	<div class="cta-container">
		<div class="features-list">
			<h2>Ready to Join the Experience?</h2>
			<p class="subheading">Limited spots available - secure your place today</p>

			<div class="features">
